choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today.
Here's a sample meal plan that includes balanced nutrition and is low in fat:
Breakfast: Oatmeal with fruit (banana, strawberries) and nuts (walnuts or almonds).
Lunch: Grilled chicken breast with steamed vegetables (carrots, broccoli), brown rice, and a side salad.
Snack: Apple slices with peanut butter.
Dinner: Baked fish (salmon) with roasted sweet potatoes and green beans.
Remember to stay hydrated throughout the day by drinking plenty of water!
